00:55:05.760 --> 00:55:07.480
Do you know him. Master?

557
00:55:11.520 --> 00:55:13.240
Show your friend to the room.

558
00:55:13.320 --> 00:55:15.960
Whatever you need. help yourself.

559
00:55:17.080 --> 00:55:19.360
We need to talk tonight.

560
00:55:19.440 --> 00:55:20.720
Okay.

561
00:55:39.160 --> 00:55:40.200
Come on.

562
00:55:53.480 --> 00:55:54.640
Jet.

563
00:55:54.720 --> 00:55:56.840
is Master always this cold?

564
00:55:59.160 --> 00:56:00.840
Wellâ€¦

565
00:56:00.920 --> 00:56:01.840
No.

566
00:56:06.360 --> 00:56:07.760
He's usually worse than this.

567
00:56:07.840 --> 00:56:09.280
This is soft.

568
00:56:17.960 --> 00:56:20.080
But don't worry.

569
00:56:20.960 --> 00:56:22.160
He might look cold.

570
00:56:22.800 --> 00:56:25.000
but if someone's in trouble.

571
00:56:25.760 --> 00:56:26.920
he always helps.

572
00:56:41.960 --> 00:56:43.600
I feel like I'm a burden.

573
00:56:45.440 --> 00:56:46.440
I should'veâ€¦

574
00:56:48.120 --> 00:56:49.800
never come here in the first place.

575
00:56:49.880 --> 00:56:52.240
Come on. you're not a burden.

576
00:56:52.320 --> 00:56:53.720
Get some sleep.

577
00:57:08.120 --> 00:57:10.960
Hey. where are you going?

578
00:57:13.520 --> 00:57:14.360
To face my karma.

579
00:57:33.840 --> 00:57:35.440
Haven't been beaten in so long.

580
00:57:37.080 --> 00:57:38.360
I miss the good old days.

581
00:57:38.440 --> 00:57:39.800
How about another one?

582
00:57:39.880 --> 00:57:41.720
You just never listen to me.

583
00:57:41.800 --> 00:57:43.880
I told you to stay out of it.

584
00:57:45.200 --> 00:57:46.040
Wellâ€¦

585
00:57:47.280 --> 00:57:49.440
Khem's a good guy.

586
00:57:55.160 --> 00:57:57.280
When I first met him.

587
00:57:57.360 --> 00:57:59.080
it felt likeâ€¦

588
00:57:59.160 --> 00:58:00.600
we'd known each other forever.

589
00:58:07.920 --> 00:58:08.760
By the way.

590
00:58:09.560 --> 00:58:11.160
that spirit you drove awayâ€¦

591
00:58:11.240 --> 00:58:12.840
Was he Khem's karmic enemy?

592
00:58:13.960 --> 00:58:14.880
No.

593
00:58:17.120 --> 00:58:18.400
Now.

594
00:58:18.480 --> 00:58:20.880
remember those frenzied spirits?

595
00:58:22.080 --> 00:58:24.520
His true karmic enemy

596
00:58:24.600 --> 00:58:26.560
has the power to control them all.

597
00:58:33.560 --> 00:58:34.560
It's gone this far.

598
00:58:35.080 --> 00:58:36.480
You still want to help him?

599
00:58:42.400 --> 00:58:43.360
Yes.

600
00:58:44.440 --> 00:58:46.040
I stand by my words.

601
00:58:49.480 --> 00:58:50.920
Please help him. Master.

602
00:58:52.840 --> 00:58:53.840
If you don't.

603
00:58:54.520 --> 00:58:55.960
I'm leaking your number.

604
00:59:11.280 --> 00:59:13.480
I won't promise I can save him.

605
00:59:17.600 --> 00:59:19.480
You'd better go keep him safe.

606
00:59:23.720 --> 00:59:25.120
The night's far from over.

607
00:59:40.760 --> 00:59:42.640
Master seems to care about Khem though.

608
00:59:43.800 --> 00:59:45.440
Didn't he say he wouldn'tâ€¦

609
00:59:47.200 --> 00:59:49.360
We'd better be ready too.

610
01:00:41.360 --> 01:00:42.920
Be careful.

611
01:00:44.200 --> 01:00:45.120
Don't worry.

612
01:00:59.680 --> 01:01:00.640
He's on his way.

613
01:01:00.720 --> 01:01:02.360
- He's here.
- That's him.

614
01:01:02.440 --> 01:01:03.520
Here he is.

615
01:01:03.600 --> 01:01:04.760
- Hey.
- Mister.

616
01:01:04.840 --> 01:01:05.680
Is everyone here?

617
01:01:05.760 --> 01:01:06.960
- Yeah. Mister.
- Yes.

618
01:01:07.040 --> 01:01:07.920
- Let's go.
- Okay.

619
01:01:08.000 --> 01:01:09.120
- All right.
- Go.

620
01:01:17.360 --> 01:01:18.920
Everyone. are you ready?

621
01:01:19.000 --> 01:01:19.920
- Yes.
- We are.

622
01:01:20.000 --> 01:01:20.920
Let's do it.

623
01:01:39.480 --> 01:01:40.760
They're here.

624
01:02:30.000 --> 01:02:31.760
Are you looking for me?

625
01:03:16.840 --> 01:03:18.200
<i>What has he done to you?</i>

626
01:03:18.280 --> 01:03:19.520
<i>Can't you just let him go?</i>

627
01:03:19.600 --> 01:03:23.160
<i>I shall never let him go.</i>

628
01:03:23.240 --> 01:03:24.400
This is Charn.

629
01:03:24.480 --> 01:03:25.560
also a junior.

630
01:03:25.640 --> 01:03:27.000
This is Jet. my best friend.

631
01:03:29.560 --> 01:03:31.760
<i>We've passed this bamboo grove</i>
<i>over and over.</i>

632
01:03:35.240 --> 01:03:36.480
<i>My duty</i>

633
01:03:36.560 --> 01:03:38.280
<i>is to take care of this village.</i>

634
01:03:38.360 --> 01:03:43.000
I'll do whatever it takes
to stop being an outsider in your eyes.
